snippet.title: Evil Officer - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Evil Officer is ready to HAUNT you again!!

See how much is enhanced in this PC version coming on 18 August 2023.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2461600?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=summer_sale&utm_medium=web

Note: The release date was delayed to 18 August due to technical issues.
